Now  feel so proud and I don't feel so sad as I born as a minority in my country.  Am so happy how big my Ethnic is with various branches. Also happy that our 4 language people have a same base in our origin. Also I don't find difficult in watching Kanara ,Malayalam, Telugu movies as they have similar words in Tamil It is easy for me too under stand also.These makes me happy

Haresh Karkar without special effects the video would be boring. So, special effects are an important part of songs & movies. There are skilled professionals (artists/designers) who edit each frame of the song or the movie after the shooting is done in the editing room. Have you ever seen them working on their workstation? Editing each frame and to have the final output in the mind by juggling the worm's eye view plus the bird's eye view is not easy. There would be multiple designers working on the same scene with different time frames. The color coordinates and the styling of the effect have to match with the one that the art director would have provided his/her directions with.  We never see the darkroom these designers spent their time perfecting the color coordinates and simply enjoy the song and move on to seeing some other songs. These artists work 14-16 hours if the project has serious deadlines. Now, that's some awesome work they do. Hat's off to them for doing such an amazing job for providing as aesthetically & appealing output!  One love to all the passionate,  hardworking and dedicated designers and artists!
